Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.230 --> 00:00:04.880
Progressive web app should be reliable,
fast, and engaging.

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:10.071
So far, you've learned techniques
acquired to make them reliable and fast.

00:00:10.071 --> 00:00:14.945
And you've used your new found skills
to build a weather app that works

00:00:14.945 --> 00:00:18.280
whether or not your users are online.

00:00:18.280 --> 00:00:22.420
And it even works on flaky networks,
thanks to service workers.

00:00:22.420 --> 00:00:27.185
By using different caching techniques,
your app get data on screen fast.

00:00:28.390 --> 00:00:30.500
Service workers are pretty amazing and

00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:35.190
we've only just touched on some of
the possibilities that they unlock.

00:00:35.190 --> 00:00:39.170
In the next section, we're going to
take a look at the techniques required

00:00:39.170 --> 00:00:42.515
to make a progressive web
app engaging and integrated.

